INTENSIFIES AND BECOMES 1040 BY 1800 UTC ON WEDNESDAY THE 1ST OF MARCH. STRG
WINDS INITIALLY IN THAMES DOVER AND WIGHT. THESE WINDS GRADUALLY EASE FM
THE E CEASING IN THAMES BY MONDAY MORNING BUT REMAINING IN THE S AND W
